body:
### Welcome to some of my MyRepo site.
This repository is intended to show some of project while in school and other personal ones. I hope it helps someone to achieve or learn a bit more of C++, Java or Objective-C:

```
$ cd JV17/MyRepo
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Sections
 C++,
 Java,
 Objective-C Development...

### About,
 Personal projects in different programming languages.
 Examples where I try to explain who some programming concepts work.
 Assignments from some of my different programming subjects.
 Some pratice in different programming languages which, I did while in school.
 My Tests and Exams preparations, and sometimes I wrote some solutions after taken the exam to verify my answers.

### Authors and Contributors
Just me @JV17. Please visit my personal website http://jorgedeveloper.com to know more about my experience and other projects publish on my personal blog http://jorgedeveloper.com/blog/.
